  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will include a translation of the Central Sensisization Inventory into French and a
      cultural validation of the French version of the questionnaire (Reliability, discrimination
      and comparison with other questionnaires).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
