        3 groups:

        Fibromyalgia Patients (group 1) Acute or subacute Ankle Sprain (Group 2) Healthy Volunteers
        (Group 3)
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical Diagnosis of Fibromyalgia (Group 1)

          -  Clinical Diagnosis of a Acute of Subacute Ankle Spain (Group 2)

          -  Healthy Volunteer (Group 3)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Having any chronic pain (group 1 and group 2)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
